#### [NEW] [formatting.py](file:///e:/miniproject/aloa/utils/formatting.py)
- Rich `Table`, `Panel`, `Tree`, `Progress` wrappers
- Color-coded status indicators (🟢 good, 🟡 warning, 🔴 critical)
